Interface IProductIdentificationHandler

All Known Subinterfaces:
IProductIdentificationPlugin
All Known Implementing Classes:
ProductIdentifierAmazon, ProductIdentifierGoogle, ProductIdentifierUPCSearchDotOrg
public interface IProductIdentificationHandler

Defines an interface for handling the action of identifying a product from the web.

Method Summary
 Product handle(java.lang.String barcode)
          The class that implements this interface will attempt to handle the identification request on its own, but will pass the request along to the next plugin if no result is found.
 

Method Detail

handle

Product handle(java.lang.String barcode)
The class that implements this interface will attempt to handle the identification request on its own, but will pass the request along to the next plugin if no result is found.

Parameters:
barcode - a string representing the barcode of the product to be identified.
Returns:
a Product instance with the located information, or null.
